,"uid":73830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000110_d49440bb8c40207453c7543ff8531b7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000110_d49440bb8c40207453c7543ff8531b7b.jpg&h=c3ff11cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe5a3cf7f0b4728566b5f27c9414ad33c9fd0b60","tid":385920,"uid":132632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:49:46.000Z","msg":"喂，個雷xx同佢地同一組黎嫁咼，did did姐點做野嫁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/004805_eef7823c9b2fea9addbdafaa076efb80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F004805_eef7823c9b2fea9addbdafaa076efb80.jpg&h=27066427&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f18410fac6db19136844a4be19769fa2646c9de4","tid":385920,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"港姐2017冠軍 雷莊𠒇老豆原來係億萬富豪<br />\n<br />\n香港小姐2017終於塵埃落定，冠軍由23歲來自多倫多的雷莊𠒇，原來老豆雷葆文係香港的十大傑出設計師， 人稱「設計多面手」，而且身家十分富有，香港及海外都擁有物業，傳聞係億億聲，在商界有頭有面。雷莊𠒇曾表示父親十分支持她參選，當然佢自己都十分有料到，作為唯一嘅海外突入佳麗，身高成5呎7寸，身材更加是十分惹火，因為佢係模特兒出身㗎！"},{"pid":"a991a1a183362eb47478c7254c3cb1313d9b5963","tid":385920,"uid":142725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吾你老母<br />\n<br />\n連登冇人屌？</blockquote><br />\n55</blockquote><br />\n5你老母 吾你老母 死返入你老母個閪度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada0b40c552b091004978762fd66446b1ccb245","tid":385920,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"她又開估雷莊𠒇的「𠒇」字之謎，她說：「其實我當年攞身份證嗰陣一直冇發覺，原來喺嗰刻已經寫錯咗，到我參選，我仲問大會做乜寫錯我名，佢哋話係跟住我身份證咁寫，我先發覺寫錯咗，我遲啲會去改番！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢文盲"}]}